sampleRecord.body_description:
Experience the glamour of the French Riviera in this stunning vacation rental. Perfect for those seeking luxury and Mediterranean charm.

THE SPACE

This beautiful property captures the essence of the French Riviera with elegant furnishings, stunning views, and access to the region's famous beaches and attractions.

GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire property including outdoor spaces and all amenities.

OTHER THINGS TO NOTE

Located in one of the world's most glamorous destinations, this property offers easy access to beaches, casinos, and the vibrant nightlife of the French Riviera.
